Fourth Department,

September, 1959

(September 11, 1959) Mary A. Leotta, Individually and as Administratrix of the Estate of Alfred R. Leotta, Deceased, Respondent, v. Joseph E. Plessinger et al., Appellants.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — Kimball, J. P., Williams, Bastow, Goldman and Halpern, JJ.
